--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This software is designed to generate commands for, and interoperate with, the
following projects. These projects are NOT bundled in this repository; they are
referenced and/or used as runtime dependencies and remain under their own
respective licenses and copyrights.

- Network Sketcher
  https://github.com/cisco-open/network-sketcher
  The open-source Cisco network-documentation tool that this extension targets.

- Cisco Modeling Labs (CML)
  https://developer.cisco.com/modeling-labs/
  The network simulation platform used as the input data source.

Runtime Python dependencies (installed separately via pip; see
cml_converter/requirements.txt). Each retains its own license:

- PyYAML
  https://pyyaml.org/
  YAML parsing of CML lab files.

- ciscoconfparse2
  https://github.com/mpenning/ciscoconfparse2
  Optional, recommended parsing of Cisco running-configurations.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Validation data
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Conversion behaviour was validated against public sample labs from:

- CiscoDevNet/cml-community
  https://github.com/CiscoDevNet/cml-community

No third-party lab content is redistributed in this repository.
